NAME
  vtkSHYXDataSetToPartitionedCollection
DESCRIPTION
  "Split vtkDataSet into a vtkPartitionedDataSetCollection: tetrahedra (object_id=1), then surface with feature-angle splitting and connectivity partitions (object_id increments)."
GROUPS
  Meshing
DEPENDS
  VTK::CommonCore
  VTK::CommonDataModel
  VTK::CommonExecutionModel
  VTK::FiltersCore
  VTK::FiltersExtraction
  VTK::FiltersGeometry
  VTK::IOIOSS
